{"tid":1552902,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"係時候諗下喺不被捕嘅情況下有咩下一步行動","createTime":"2019-09-08T12:28:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T20:15:12.000Z","uid":309002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"15b36b0d62af7e33ac8f0f2160d8f3d0208789d7","tid":1552902,"uid":309002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T12:28:32.000Z","msg":"而家濫捕越黎越嚴重<br />\n地鐵站打人拉人已成常態<br />\n地鐵站靜坐都要封站出防暴趕<br />\n入機場靜坐途中就要拉<br />\n經過有警察嘅地方都要拉<br />\n今日開始連路人都拉<br />\n唔想再有人受傷同被捕<br />\n一個都不能少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n太子站831呢件事要有更多人關注<br />\n就一定要搵立法會議員幫<br />\n保護知情人士同source來源之下逼地鐵同政府<br />\n交代同公開831太子同荔枝角嘅cctv<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">每日出黎圍地鐵站已經解決唔到問題<br />\n只會有更多人被捕<br />\n越係打壓就要搵其他方法</span></strong><br />\n逼政府講出真相<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a34adfafca4cf7ac32b6a68c9d940a1362f76f1","tid":1552902,"uid":309002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T12:28:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a301b1f02624375faebcf64b1c914e72cc64a7d3","tid":1552902,"uid":309002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T12:28:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3042d59b0f8258b20250d65f1fc7367029b1a064","tid":1552902,"uid":309002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T12:29:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b3228fa020b3e3f864f9239811e027647840e796","tid":1552902,"uid":309002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T12:29:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"57e83cc848d3820fb3e52e95e8e452f69f7edb0f","tid":1552902,"uid":309002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T12:29:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"af3b61f152657bfe2e111a83e0150e12a15f2303","tid":1552902,"uid":309002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T12:29:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f6e49d16a2f3b9295a2ee2f4c3e515021d021161","tid":1552902,"uid":309002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"c